sequenceDiagram
    title InfoHub 设备-后端-CRS-Sub2API 调用链路

    participant Device as Device<br/>ESPHome 墨水屏
    participant Backend as Backend<br/>InfoHub Server
    participant CRS as CRS<br/>Claude Relay
    participant Sub2API as Sub2API<br/>Codex Proxy

    %% Background data collection
    loop Every 10 min (Cron Scheduler)

        par Claude Relay Collection
            Backend->>Backend: Trigger ClaudeRelayCollector

            Backend->>CRS: POST /web/auth/login
            CRS-->>Backend: Bearer Token

            Backend->>CRS: GET /admin/claude-accounts
            CRS-->>Backend: Account List (active only)

            Backend->>CRS: GET /admin/claude-accounts/usage
            CRS-->>Backend: Quota & Usage Data

            Note over Backend: Parse quota (5h/7d window)<br/>Extract token usage & costs

            Backend->>Backend: Save DataItems to SQLite

        and Sub2API Collection
            Backend->>Backend: Trigger Sub2APICollector

            Backend->>Sub2API: POST /login (credentials)
            Sub2API-->>Backend: Bearer Token

            Backend->>Sub2API: GET /api/v1/admin/accounts<br/>?platform=openai&type=oauth&status=active
            Sub2API-->>Backend: Account List + IDs

            Backend->>Sub2API: POST /api/v1/admin/accounts<br/>/today-stats/batch {account_ids}
            Sub2API-->>Backend: Daily Stats (tokens, costs)

            Note over Backend: Parse quota (5h/7d window)<br/>Extract token usage & costs

            Backend->>Backend: Save DataItems to SQLite

        end

    end

    %% Device request flow
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Device,Backend: On-Demand Device Request

        Device->>Backend: GET /dashboard/eink/device.json?token=xxx

        Backend->>Backend: Authenticate dashboard token

        Backend->>Backend: Read snapshots from Store

        Note over Backend: buildEInkDevicePayload()<br/>Aggregate claude_relay + sub2api

        Backend-->>Device: JSON Response<br/>{claude, codex, total, refreshSeconds}

        Note over Device: Render on e-ink display
    end
